国&rdquo;，枫叶国的枫糖也是鼎鼎大名、必备的伴手礼。而在加东能够体验一把地道的加拿大式农家乐，也是很有滋味的一种玩法。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">在传统的枫糖木屋里，参观古老的制作工坊，和匠人们交流，和朋友们分享，和孩子们一起欢笑。冬日里大概没有比这更简单浪漫的事情了。</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 36px 0px 22px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 700 18px/30px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">3、瀑布葡萄园</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img onerror=\"javascript:errorimg.call(this);\" alt=\"加东冬季嘉年华：冰宫酒店、枫糖小木屋、瀑布葡萄园...\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/134c00054ff9f0bce930\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"426\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 1em auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: n