px; margin: 1em auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" />普吉岛JW万豪度假酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">地处尚未受到开发的迈考海滩的边沿地带，客房设计时尚精美，室内米色调的装饰温馨宜人，在房间里就可以一览着美丽的安达曼海景，最特别的岩石泳池美轮美奂，原生态、质朴休闲。这里靠近sirinath国家海洋公园与海龟产卵区，还可以吃到精美的泰式、日式、意大利等美食。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img onerror=\"javascript:errorimg.call(this);\" alt=\"普吉岛7大浪漫蜜月度假酒店\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/f7c000207458fe9d24b\" img_width=\"991\" img_height=\"585\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 1em auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" />普吉岛艾美海滩度假酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">这是一家海滨现代化酒店，位于普吉岛西南部、卡伦海滩北部，环境宁静，富有美丽的泰式风格和别具特色的异国情调，泰式装修，主要以木与丝绸为主。酒店有多家餐厅，提供各式菜肴，从池边小吧，到日式、意大利、海鲜自助餐与亚洲小吃等。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img onerror=\"javascript:errorimg.call(this);\" alt=\"普吉岛7大浪漫蜜月度假酒店\" src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/f770002854a9fe3f455\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 1em auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" />以上就是第六感小编为大家介绍的普吉岛7大浪漫蜜月度假酒店，这些酒店都是非常浪漫的，若是你喜欢浪漫也是可以去体验的哟!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">结语：度假旅游是人们生活不可或缺的部分，人们在节假日或是周末的时候都是会选择出去旅游的。而对于旅游的目的地的选择人们也是会根据季节等等因素而决定的，而结婚的蜜月之旅更是会非常慎重的，普吉岛就是一个非常好的选择哟!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a href=\"http://zglyjdw.cdsxwy.cc\">中国旅游酒店网</a></p>', '', '', '', '1', '1', '1471403130', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('10', '4', '外出旅游住酒店 这几个小细节您多留意', '<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">近年来，越来越多的市民可能会选择来趟出国游。出国旅游，肯定会涉及到住宿问题。对于一些首次出国旅游或旅游经验不太丰富的&ldquo;菜鸟&rdquo;来说，入住进酒店后，有一些小细节需要多留意。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">想睡个懒觉记得挂上&ldquo;请勿打扰&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">一般酒店中，房门的门把上都会挂有&ldquo;请勿打扰&rdquo;的牌子。如果前一天游玩比较累，想在酒店房间好好睡个懒觉的话，记得在关门前，要在门外把这个牌子挂上。因为酒店的客房保洁人员每天上午都会主动进入旅客的房间进行卫生清理，更换床单等工作，当他们看到&ldquo;请勿打扰&rdquo;的牌子后，自然会绕道走开。如果没挂&ldquo;请勿打扰&rdquo;的牌子，就有可能出现您还在床上熟睡，保洁人员却突然闯进来的尴尬情况。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img onerror=\"javascript:errorimg.call(this);\" alt=\"外出旅游住酒店 这几个小细节您多留意\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3e60001b677ce0b5df0\" img_width=\"533\" img_height=\"280\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 1em auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">&ldquo;付费&rdquo;遥控器按钮您别碰</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">有些游客由于不懂外文，常常在酒店看电视节目的时候误入&ldquo;收费&rdquo;电视频道而遭受损失。在国外的酒店房间里，基本上所有的电视一开机都处于&ldquo;收费&rdquo;电视的默认状态，只要按下诸如：&ldquo;ENTER&rdquo;（确认）、&ldquo;PAY&rdquo;（付费）、&ldquo;有料&rdquo;（日文付费的意思）等按键，您就会进入&ldquo;付费&rdquo;电视频道。如果您根本就不想收看&ldquo;收费&rdquo;电视节目，那么就要注意不要乱按酒店电视遥控器上的按键。如果是跟团出游，入住酒店前可提前咨询一下导游。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">屋内的饮料先问清是否收费</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">现在国外很多4星及4星以上的高端酒店，都会在房间配备&ldquo;迷你吧&rdquo;（Mini Bar），房间内不但会有个小吧台，还会有个小冰箱，里面会供应各式各样的果汁饮料、咖啡、高端洋酒、小零食等。但是这些食物或饮品一般都是要收费的，而且价格还都不菲。没经验的游客要是不想花冤枉钱，最好不要动它们或者提前咨询导游、酒店前台，问清哪些是免费物品，哪些是收费物品。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a href=\"http://zglyjdw.cdsxwy.cc\">中国旅游酒店网</a></p>', '', '', '', '1', '1', '1471403205', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('11', '4', '三亚7家顶级酒店，你去过几家？', '<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">安纳塔拉：有顶级SPA的5星酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134a000128e108fa0d81?imageView2/2/w/2000/h/1200\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 478px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134a000128e108fa0d81?imageView2/2/w/2000/h/1200\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">三亚半山半岛安纳塔拉度假酒店，是起源于泰国的5星度假村，旗下的Anantara Spa是亚洲顶级Spa的代名词，这座泰式风味的度假酒店位于大东海的半山腰处，背山临海，靠近鹿回头山顶公园。 Spa是这座酒店的灵魂，安纳塔拉的Spa在香熏按摩的基础上加入印度香料，有宁神之效。除了Spa，酒店的餐厅也是一大亮点，有泰式美食，也有三亚小吃，西式大餐自然也不差。此外，酒店有免费的儿童娱乐项目，而且每天不重样，也是亲子游好去处。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">鸟巢：舒淇葛优的试婚酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134c00044e29517ab0df?imageView2/2/w/800/h/533\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 531px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134c00044e29517ab0df?imageView2/2/w/800/h/533\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">三亚人间天堂鸟巢度假村因《非诚勿扰2》而大热，舒淇和葛优的试婚房就是这家酒店的一间。酒店在亚龙湾热带森林公园内部，所有客房以飞禽命名，极尽野趣奢华。 度假村分东园和西园，所有鸟巢客房栖居于丛林之上，可远眺亚龙湾，鸟巢住客还能免费游览公园，只要早起就能避开人流静享美景。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">康莱德：被TVB青睐的别墅酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134a000128e087b0932b?imageView2/2/w/1200/h/720\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 478px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134a000128e087b0932b?imageView2/2/w/1200/h/720\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">三亚海棠湾康莱德酒店是TVB人气剧集《冲上云霄2》在三亚的取景地。据说酒店的8888号房是万达贵公子的定点聚会所。这里离免税店也很近，可谓是土豪必选酒店之一。 康莱德是希尔顿旗下的高端酒店品牌，酒店以别墅为主，部分客房还有专门泳池，私密性好。这里共有四家餐厅，从粤菜到法餐都能尝到，不用怕路远，去哪儿都有免费的电瓶车接送。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">珊瑚酒店：蜈支洲岛最奢酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134b000561adc7185164?imageView2/2/w/1926/h/1155\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 478px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134b000561adc7185164?imageView2/2/w/1926/h/1155\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">三亚蜈支洲岛珊瑚酒店是蜈支洲岛上唯一一家五星酒店，位于岛的西北角。 蜈支洲岛晚上五点左右游客就散了，之后就是岛上住客的浪漫时光。若是愿意早起，还可以去岛上的观日岩看日出。酒店本身有设计出众的泳池，另外还专门辟出一块散养鸡、鸭的亲子乐园，适合亲子出行的游客。 预订酒店的住客从码头上岛有专门的VIP通道，不需要等待，上岛后有免费电瓶车接送到酒店。此外也有免费班车接送亚龙湾和凤凰国际机场等目的地。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">莱佛士：远离人潮的超星级酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134c00044e2afc66cf26?imageView2/2/w/1131/h/678\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 478px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/134c00044e2afc66cf26?imageView2/2/w/1131/h/678\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">海南雅居乐莱佛士酒店位于远离市区的清水湾，比起亚龙湾、海棠湾清静很多，距离最近的市镇15分钟车程，住在这里最重要的事，就是静静享受阳光和沙滩。 作为超星级的酒店，硬件实在无可挑剔，酒店有32间奢华私人别墅，均含独立泳池，透过观景落地窗和私人露台可把南海风光一览无余。 住在这个偌大的独立王国也不用愁闷，临近酒店有2个18洞的顶级高尔夫球场、雅居乐清水湾游艇会，而且酒店每天有免费穿梭巴士至机场，途经免税店等购物地。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">悦榕庄：背山面海的老牌奢华酒店</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/13490000ec74e88551bf?imageView2/2/w/2532/h/1519\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 478px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/13490000ec74e88551bf?imageView2/2/w/2532/h/1519\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">三亚悦榕庄是老牌五星奢华酒店，光是悦榕庄这个牌子就足以保证它的品质。酒店位于鹿回头湾，毗邻鹿回头公园，背山面海，风景独好。 酒店别墅有带泳池的房间，泳池水24小时循环，别墅被小型园林分割，私密性很好。著名的悦榕SPA、海岛风味的美食，也是人们选择悦榕庄的理由。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">御海棠：来自喜达屋的顶级品牌</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"image_con loaded\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; widows: 1; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px auto 12px 40px; min-height: 100px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; background: rgb(255,255,255); color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image-source: url(https://tms3.bytecdn.cn/dist/online/toutiao/public/img/border_f0441f1.png); border-image-slice: 2; border-image-repeat: stretch\"><img class=\"image lazy\" alt=\"\" data-original=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/13490000ec75019d985e?imageView2/2/w/1641/h/984\" style=\"border-bottom-style: none; margin: auto; border-left-style: none; width: 798px; display: block; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; height: 478px; border-right-style: none\" src=\"https://p3a.bytecdn.cn/large/13490000ec75019d985e?imageView2/2/w/1641/h/984\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">喜达屋集团的顶级酒店品牌，位于相对安静的海棠湾，和蜈支洲岛隔海相望，酒店背靠翠绿的山峦，独享几百米米长的迷人海滩。 酒店的客房注重细节，色调和纹理都与周围环境相配，落地窗设计，可供客人享受宽阔的海景。此外，酒店内还有儿童俱乐部，配有艺术工艺角和儿童嬉水池，适合带小朋友来共享亲子时光。 在御海棠的全日餐厅能吃到纯正东南亚美食、传统海南特色佳肴和地道的西班牙美味。在三叶梅大堂吧，可以品尝到特制鸡尾酒、现磨香浓咖啡以及顶级葡萄酒。</p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 12px 0px 12px 40px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 18px/27px STHeiti, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a href=\"http://zglyjdw.cdsxwy.cc \">中国旅游酒店网</a></p>', '', '', '', '1', '1', '1471403283', '', '0', 'http://', '');
INSERT INTO `ecs_article` ( `article_id`, `cat_id`, `title`, `content`, `author`, `author_email`, `keywords`, `article_type`, `is_open`, `add_time`, `file_url`, `open_type`, `link`, `description` ) VALUES  ('13', '4', '未来十年：中国酒店将向精品个性化发展', '<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">无论是外资酒店或是内资酒店，将来开业的酒店将多以奢华型的精品或度假酒店为主。这些精品、度假酒店区别于传统高端酒店&ldquo;千店一面&rdquo;的模式，每家酒店都将极具个性化地创造出自己的特色。在高端酒店数量过剩的情况下，真正注重&ldquo;体验&rdquo;的奢华型酒店将引发酒店投资的新热潮。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px\"><img onerror=\"javascript:errorimg.call(this);\" alt=\"未来十年：中国酒店将向精品个性化发展\" src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/339000eafdb9871ba70\" img_width=\"500\" img_height=\"300\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; border-left: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em auto; letter-spacing: normal; display: block; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">度假、精品型酒店投资渐热</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">大家知道，五星级酒店和奢华酒店是两个概念，五星级酒店可以包含奢华酒店，但奢华酒店不一定是五星级酒店，因为许多精品酒店数量很少，不够中国星级评定标准的数量，但其硬件设施的豪华程度已超越星级评定标准。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">其实，奢华型的度假酒店、精品酒店在硬件上更加个性化并具备地方特色，甚至更多地运用了酒店新技术;度假酒店以接待度假休闲游客为主，多建在自然风景区附近，远离市区，经营季节性强，对酒店区域内的环境设计要求高、对娱乐设施的配套要求较完善，讲究人与自然的充分融合;而精品酒店强调&ldquo;小而精致&rdquo;，它的客房数量不多，但其内部装修极其豪华，独具特色。精品酒店在服务上更加趋向定制化，普遍采用的是管家式服务，服务人员与客房的比例是2：1，甚至3：1，而在星级酒店，这个数字通常是1：1，最多是1.5：1。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">非个性化酒店产品泛滥</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">目前，我国并不缺乏有高消费能力的游客，也不缺乏传统高端酒店，缺少的是个性化的酒店产品。&ldquo;千店一面&rdquo;的传统高端酒店或许有足够豪华的设施，但没有持续的竞争力，到最后只能&ldquo;拼地段&rdquo;。真正的高端游客需要个性化的产品，如适合老人的、儿童的、情侣的、个性怪异的、时尚前卫的等等。现在有许多酒店打着&ldquo;超五星&rdquo;、&ldquo;白金五星&rdquo;、&ldquo;个性化&rdquo;的旗号，但其产品实质并无太大亮点。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">随着酒店行业对高端、个性化诉求的增长，越来越多的度假酒店、精品酒店品牌即将诞生。现在是市场竞争到了必须要有清晰明确定位的阶段：经济型酒店以量取胜、高端酒店则需更加个性化，相互竞争的是&ldquo;体验特色&rdquo;，这也是顺应时代发展的趋势。美国著名未来学家托夫勒在20世纪80年代发表的《第三次浪潮》中曾预言，工业化时代的规模经营将被信息化时代的多样化、多元化、个性化所取代。在酒店业，设计师酒店、奢侈品牌酒店、精品酒店、主题酒店将层出不穷与之呼应。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">小型精品酒店方兴未艾</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">数据显示，中国酒店客源正从商务75%、休闲25%演变为商务50%、休闲50%的比例;从观光80%、度假20%演变到观光40%、度假60%，度假需求成为新热点。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">酒店的&ldquo;奢华&rdquo;很难用量化去衡量，客房数量不多但个性奢华的精品酒店将在未来迎来较大的发展空间。这些酒店在建好之后，真正追求的是服务的差异化和更加贴心、管家式的高端的服务理念，&ldquo;体验&rdquo;将成为高端酒店的核心。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">目前中国酒店投资的&ldquo;奢华酒店热&rdquo;、&ldquo;精品酒店热&rdquo;类似于美国十年前的酒店行业。2003年，美国精品酒店的客房占1%、收入占3%，6-8年即可收回投资，而传统高端酒店需要10-15年。精品及设计型酒店自2008年开始，在中国的客房量每年都以30%以上的速度增长，当下酒店开发商的报告中有65%的结论是建小型精品酒店。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">轻资产重扩张的失意</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">很长一段时间以来，国际酒店品牌以输出品牌、收取管理费的轻资产运作模式在国内飞速扩展，但这种模式如今在国内遇到了阻碍。日前，北京北辰实业股份有限公司与洲际酒店集团长达十年的管理合约到期，业主方北辰实业股份有限公司没有选择续签合同。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">洲际集团这次与业主方分手尚显平和，回顾近几年，洲际、万豪、雅高等以轻资产模式扩展的大型酒店集团，纷纷出现撤牌情况。万豪集团2008-2011年曾连续三年从北京撤店。受到经济下行及政策影响，奢华酒店的入住率和房价持续下滑，中方业主在缴纳了高额管理费的情况下，却得不到预期利润，这导致了业主方与管理方的矛盾显现。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">此外，随着中国房地产市场的火爆、酒店大规模的扩容，外资酒店集团逐渐在追求短期效益和长远口碑的关系中产生动摇，很多跨国酒店品牌放低了管理门槛。一位外资酒店管理人员坦言，&ldquo;高速扩张让管理水准下降，包括人力资源、后台支撑等都有所削弱&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">外资品牌餐饮不够&ldquo;本土化&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">数据显示，民族酒店餐饮方面的收入占收入总额55%左右，餐饮做得最好的香格里拉，平均餐饮收入也只能占总额35%-38%，一般的外资酒店都不会超过30%。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">对于大多数外资酒店来说，餐饮很难成为它们的强项。这其中的核心原因是，国际酒店集团的餐饮业务被当做酒店管理经营的附属，在观念上没有十分重视。对于外资酒店来说，酒店预算决定一切，成本效益分析和投资回报率分析都会促使酒店管理集团将重心放在酒店客房销售业务上，因为只有这样才能实现营业利润总额，快速达到酒店管理集团获得管理费用的标准。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">过于坚守&ldquo;境外标准&rdquo;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">据悉，国际酒店集团的基本管理费一般为年营业额的5%-8%，奖励管理费按一定比例从利润中递进提取，利润越高比例也越高。此外，国际酒店集团派驻的管理团队都按&ldquo;境外标准&rdquo;支付薪酬，这份薪资也要由业主方承担。有些国际品牌酒店的管理费用和薪资甚至占到酒店年收入的三成。关注&ldquo;大海、旅游、人&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">令酒店业主郁闷的是，他们给着&ldquo;境外标准&rdquo;的管理费，却得不到&ldquo;境外标准&rdquo;的管理。随着中国酒店大规模扩容，很多跨国酒店集团追求短期效益，放低了管理门槛。为此，外资酒店品牌与本土开发商的矛盾日深，并连续曝出&ldquo;分手&rdquo;事件。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">目前来看，北京乃至全国的高端酒店市场仍旧为外资酒店所主导。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">中国旅游会统计数据显示，截至2012年10月，全国共有717家五星级饭店，国际品牌所管理的饭店约200家。在717家五星级饭店中，星级评分在440分以上的饭店约15%，即108家左右，主要为国际品牌管理;北京市62家五星级饭店中，国际品牌管理的饭店为29家，接近一半，除个别饭店外，市中心高端饭店几乎全部为国际品牌管理。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">我们认为，虽然高端酒店市场中外资品牌管理着五星级中最好的饭店，但本土公司已开始尝试进入高端五星级市场，未来一两年，内资酒店与外资酒店的攻防战将全面打响。在这一市场中，外资品牌受益于其传统优势，主要采用委托管理模式，而本土集团则充分利用雄厚的资本实力，采取了资产支撑品牌的策略，以加强对品牌创建初期的支持力度。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">内资品牌管理文化差距大</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">目前，中国酒店行业的客房接待、内部功能以及豪华指数等&ldquo;硬件设施&rdquo;已经国际化，只是酒店的管理和文化等&ldquo;软件&rdquo;还与国外的水平存在很大差距。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">内资酒店的很大一部分源于国有资产，是地方政府或国有集团所属的酒店，而酒店的经营与运作的核心管理层却大都是任命制，这些管理层或管理层上级的思想观念几乎还是源于传统的计划经济体系，大都缺乏市场观念，并不以企业经营好坏为第一考核指标，一切凭借着酒店管理层的事业心、责任心或良心在经营酒店，如遇到缺乏创新的管理团队，酒店的经营自然逊色。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 400\">缺乏营销意识</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">国内酒店业高层缺乏整体营销意识，大都还停留在与会议公司、旅行机构的合作上，并未展开全面营销，这让店销售或市场人员无从了解企业营销方向，无法展开营销的整体思路和规划。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">其主要表现在缺乏整体销售策划、缺乏销售的执行计划、缺乏销售渠道、缺乏品牌或媒体支持等方面。相当长一段时间，内资酒店的宣传主要集中在旅游公司的广告上，让人感觉国内酒店业似乎已经成了旅游公司的附属品。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">其实，从内资管理酒店品牌名称来看，什么&ldquo;嘉华&rdquo;、&ldquo;丽雅&rdquo;、&ldquo;尚雅&rdquo;、&ldquo;瑰丽&rdquo;等等都有模仿外资酒店名称的痕迹，所以说内资在崛起，但走的路还远着哪。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">但不论如何，未来十年国内酒店内外资管理差距正在缩小，且向精品个性化发展的趋势是不变的，当然也需建造数十家客房数在2000~5000间的酒店，而无个性化的的大中型酒店将逐步萎缩。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 1; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1em 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 16px/32px \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(34,34,34); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a href=\"http://zglyjdw.cdsxwy.cc\">中国旅游酒店网</a></p>', '', '', '', '1', '1', '1471458075', '', '0', 'http://', '');
