ze: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">伦敦塔桥</span></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">伦敦塔桥是从英国伦敦泰晤士河口算起的第一座桥，也是伦敦的象征。该桥始建于</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">1886</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">年，</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">1894</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">6</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">月</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">30</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">日对公众开放，将伦敦南北区连接成整体。伦敦塔桥的设计颇为合理，在世界桥梁建筑业中有口皆碑。桥身分为上、下两层，既可以饱览泰晤士河两岸的美丽风光，也可以是供车辆通行。桥塔内设楼梯上下，内设博物馆、展览厅、商店、酒吧等。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><img data-url=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/46e0f1c656694f028fe3e2c40f40af4d.png!650w\" border=\"border=\" class=\"scrollLoading\" src=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/46e0f1c656694f028fe3e2c40f40af4d.png!650w\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 650px; display: inline;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">白金汉宫</span></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">白金汉宫</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">(Buckingham Palace</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">）英国的王宫，是一座四层楼的正方形围院建筑，保留着</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">19</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">世纪前期的建筑风格，奢华富贵的装修风格，每一处细节都展现了皇家与生俱来的气质。宫内有典礼厅、音乐厅、宴会厅、画廊等六百余个房间。白金汉宫的皇家卫队每年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">4-9&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">月时上午</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">11:30</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">至</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">12:00</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">都会举行的换岗仪式，其他月份每两天</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">11:30</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">举行一次。 如果皇宫正门上方悬挂着皇室旗帜，则表示女王正在里面，如果没有的话，那就代表女王外出。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><img data-url=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/36ff1e59de6a4aa888d4485580d54cff.jpg!650w\" border=\"border=\" class=\"scrollLoading\" src=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/36ff1e59de6a4aa888d4485580d54cff.jpg!650w\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 650px; display: inline;\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>购物推荐</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">Burberry</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">Burberry被誉为英国的国民品牌，赫敏女神的御用品牌，英国人心中的骄傲！有时在伦敦地铁里也能看到穿着Burberry风衣围着Burberry围巾的优雅的Office&nbsp;lady。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img data-url=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/81623d8b71f4447191a23707a6ad1854.jpg!650w\" border=\"border=\" class=\"scrollLoading\" src=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/81623d8b71f4447191a23707a6ad1854.jpg!650w\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 650px; display: inline;\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 20pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">Jo&nbsp;Malone</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">英国香氛世家Jo&nbsp;Malone&nbsp;London&nbsp;祖&middot;&nbsp;玛珑，以出人意料的香氛混搭和典雅的献礼美学讴歌英伦风范。除了独立店面，百货专柜和机场都有卖，优雅清新的品牌形象让许多人倾心，就连凯特王妃也拜倒其中。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<img data-url=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/eed2327394cf4db8b43c986b81f7cc3e.jpg!650w\" border=\"border=\" class=\"scrollLoading\" src=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/eed2327394cf4db8b43c986b81f7cc3e.jpg!650w\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 650px; display: inline;\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">英国茶</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;\">Whittard，始于1886年，在英国的大中城市都有其专卖店，种类齐全，从经典的英式红茶，到绿茶、白茶、花草茶、水果茶及调味茶，应有尽有。价格亲民，品种繁多。另一种更高端的品牌是Fortnum&nbsp;Mason始于1707年，一直是英国皇室的御用品牌。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; color: rgb(116, 126, 152); font-family: &quot;text-indent:0pt; background-color: #FFFFFF; text-align: justify;&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img data-url=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/0dc11546c5d149469088853e1d089b01.jpg!650w\" border=\"border=\" class=\"scrollLoading\" src=\"http://img8.yiqifei.com/20170117/0dc11546c5d149469088853e1d089b01.jpg!650w\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 650px; display: inline;\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>', 'images/201701/thumb_img/181_thumb_G_1484620555604.jpg', 'images/201701/goods_img/181_G_1484620555163.jpg', 'images/201701/source_img/181_G_1484620555007.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '59', '1484620555', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1484620555', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
